Resistance.help: Spirits are non corporeal and highly resistant to Immobilization smashing, lethal and negative energy damage. However, they are vulnerable to Energy and Psionic damage.
Resistance.shortHelp: Auto Res Smash, Lethal, Negative, Immobilize

Ethereal.help: Spirits can make themselves Ethereal and shift out of the material plane. Ethereal Spectres are invisible, and cannot affect or be affected by those in normal space.
Ethereal.targetHelp: Spirits can make themselves Ethereal and shift out of the material plane. Ethereal Spectres are invisible, and cannot affect or be affected by those in normal space.
